lambdacommon
------------------------------------------
Library written in C++ with common features

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libclambdacommon1-1.10.0-1bl2
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  liblambdacommon1-1.10.0-1bl2
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/AperLambda/lambdacommon

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/AperLambda/lambdacommon.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack lambdacommon-1.10.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./lambdacommon-1.10.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/lambdacommon-1.10.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/lambdacommon-1.10.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblambdacommon1-1.10.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liblambdacommon-devel-1.10.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libclambdacommon1-1.10.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libclambdacommon-devel-1.10.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

